---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- ═══════════════════ HERO ═══════════════════ -->
  <section id="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-left reveal">
          <div class="hero-status">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span data-i18n="hero_status">Disponible · Q3 2026</span>
          </div>
          <h1>
            <span data-i18n="hero_h1">Automatizo</span><br />
            <span class="gradient" data-i18n="hero_h2">tu ecommerce.</span>
          </h1>
          <div class="hero-role">
            <span data-i18n="hero_role">Especialista en</span>
            <span class="chip">n8n</span>
            <span class="chip">Chatwoot</span>
            <span class="chip">Shopify</span>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-bio" data-i18n="hero_bio">
            Automatizo soporte y operaciones para ecommerce en LATAM. <strong>2+ años</strong> · <strong>68+ workflows</strong> · n8n + Chatwoot + Shopify. Desde Puebla, México — remoto worldwide.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta-row">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('projects').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
              <span data-i18n="cta_work">Ver el trabajo</span>
              <span class="arr">↗</span>
            </button>
            <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="document.getElementById('contact').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
              <span data-i18n="cta_talk">Hablemos</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-right reveal">
          <div class="orb iris hero-orb" id="hero-orb">
            <div class="orb-halo"></div>
            <div class="orb-sphere"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-photo">
            <img src="/me.jpg" alt="Kevin Quiroz" width="400" height="400" fetchpriority="high" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
            <div class="caption">KQ · MX</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════ ABOUT ═══════════════════ -->
  <section id="about" class="s">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="s-head reveal">
        <span class="label" data-i18n="lbl_about">Sobre mí · 01</span>
        <h2 data-i18n="about_h">Sistemas que <span class="grad">no fallan.</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-photo-wrap reveal">
          <img src="/me.jpg" alt="Kevin Quiroz" width="400" height="500" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="about-photo-meta">
            <div class="name">Luis Kevin Quiroz Pacheco</div>
            <div class="where">Puebla, México</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-prose reveal">
          <p class="lead" data-i18n="about_lead">
            CX Operations &amp; Automation Specialist. Diseño la fontanería invisible que mantiene a los ecommerces corriendo cuando nadie está mirando.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="about_p1">
            Especializado en automatizaciones de CX con <strong>n8n, Chatwoot y Shopify</strong>. Integro APIs, webhooks y soluciones con IA para que el soporte de tus clientes escale sin escalar el equipo.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="about_p2">
            Dos años, 68 workflows en producción. La diferencia entre un demo y una operación es lo que pasa a las 3 AM cuando un cliente escala y no hay soporte disponible. <strong>Mi trabajo es que eso no ocurra.</strong>
          </p>

          <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="glass-card"><div class="n">2+</div><div class="l" data-i18n="ast_y">Años</div></div>
            <div class="glass-card"><div class="n">68+</div><div class="l" data-i18n="ast_w">Workflows</div></div>
            <div class="glass-card"><div class="n">07</div><div class="l" data-i18n="ast_p">Proyectos</div></div>
            <div class="glass-card"><div class="n">B2</div><div class="l" data-i18n="ast_l">Inglés</div></div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="tl">
              <div class="when">Oct 2025<br /><span class="now" data-i18n="now">Now</span></div>
              <div>
                <h3>CX Operations &amp; Automation Specialist</h3>
                <div class="org hl">Interprika</div>
                <ul>
                  <li data-i18n="j1b1">Automatización de operaciones de soporte con n8n, Chatwoot e IA</li>
                  <li data-i18n="j1b2">Diseño y mantenimiento de workflows de CX end-to-end</li>
                  <li data-i18n="j1b3">Integración de Shopify, APIs REST y webhooks</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl">
              <div class="when">Abr 2025<br /><span data-i18n="present">Presente</span></div>
              <div>
                <h4 data-i18n="j_free_t">Freelance Automation Specialist</h4>
                <div class="org">Autónomo</div>
                <ul>
                  <li data-i18n="j_free_b1">Jousfit: 68+ workflows — n8n · Chatwoot · Shopify · Supabase · OpenAI</li>
                  <li data-i18n="j_free_b2">Valt: marketing automation — Whisper · Mailchimp · Hotmart</li>
                  <li data-i18n="j_free_b3">n8n Bodas: CRM + scraping + email tracking para eventos</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl">
              <div class="when">Nov 2024 — Abr 2025</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Frontend Developer</h3>
                <div class="org">Bedrock Digital</div>
                <ul>
                  <li data-i18n="j2b1">Desarrollo WordPress y React.js: performance, UI/UX, responsividad</li>
                  <li data-i18n="j2b2">Integración de plugins SEO técnico</li>
                  <li data-i18n="j2b3">Implementación de layouts responsive</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl">
              <div class="when">Dic 2023 — Abr 2024</div>
              <div>
                <h4 data-i18n="j_inside_t">Business Development Specialist</h4>
                <div class="org">InsideInnovations</div>
                <ul>
                  <li data-i18n="j_inside_b1">Prospección comercial y generación de leads</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tl">
              <div class="when">2019 — 2024</div>
              <div>
                <h4 data-i18n="edu">Ing. en Sistemas Computacionales</h4>
                <div class="org">BUAP — Benemérita Universidad Autónoma de Puebla</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════ SERVICES ═══════════════════ -->
  <section id="services" class="s">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="s-head reveal">
        <span class="label" data-i18n="lbl_srv">Servicios · 02</span>
        <h2 data-i18n="srv_h">Lo que <span class="grad">construyo.</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="services">
        <article class="svc reveal">
          <div class="svc-glyph fire float float-1">
            <div class="surface">
              <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <circle cx="5" cy="5.5" r="2"/>
                <circle cx="13" cy="5.5" r="2"/>
                <circle cx="11" cy="18.5" r="2"/>
                <circle cx="19" cy="18.5" r="2"/>
                <path d="M7 5.5h4"/>
                <path d="M13 7.5v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2"/>
                <path d="M13 18.5h4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 data-i18n="svc1_t">Automatización</h3>
          <p data-i18n="svc1_p">n8n y Make. Workflows end-to-end con error handling, logs y confiabilidad de producción para ecommerce.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag">n8n</span><span class="tag">Make</span><span class="tag">Webhooks</span></div>
        </article>

        <article class="svc reveal">
          <div class="svc-glyph aqua float float-2">
            <div class="surface">
              <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M4 5 h16 a1 1 0 0 1 1 1 v9 a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1 h-9 l-4 4 v-4 h-3 a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1 v-9 a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1z"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="9" cy="10.5" r="1" stroke="none"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="12" cy="10.5" r="1" stroke="none"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="15" cy="10.5" r="1" stroke="none"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 data-i18n="svc2_t">Chatbot &amp; Soporte IA</h3>
          <p data-i18n="svc2_p">Chatwoot + OpenAI. Agentes conversacionales con handoff humano, escalamiento automático y contexto persistente.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Chatwoot</span><span class="tag">OpenAI</span><span class="tag">n8n</span></div>
        </article>

        <article class="svc reveal">
          <div class="svc-glyph violet float float-3">
            <div class="surface">
              <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M3.5 9 H17 m-3-3 l3 3 -3 3"/>
                <path d="M20.5 15 H7 m3 3 l-3-3 3-3"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 data-i18n="svc3_t">API &amp; Webhooks</h3>
          <p data-i18n="svc3_p">Conexión entre apps, sincronización en tiempo real y manejo robusto de errores.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag">REST</span><span class="tag">Webhooks</span><span class="tag">JSON</span></div>
        </article>

        <article class="svc reveal">
          <div class="svc-glyph lime float float-4">
            <div class="surface">
              <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M4 5 h16 v3 H4z"/>
                <path d="M4 10 h10 v2 H4z"/>
                <path d="M4 14 h7 v2 H4z"/>
                <circle cx="18" cy="17" r="3"/>
                <path d="M18 15.5 v1.5 h1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 data-i18n="svc4_t">Shopify &amp; Ecommerce</h3>
          <p data-i18n="svc4_p">Automatización de pedidos, soporte post-venta y detección de fraude. Shopify + Supabase + n8n.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Shopify</span><span class="tag">Supabase</span><span class="tag">n8n</span></div>
        </article>

        <article class="svc reveal">
          <div class="svc-glyph sun float float-5">
            <div class="surface">
              <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M3 18 C 6 18, 7 5, 12 5 C 17 5, 18 18, 21 18"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="3" cy="18" r="1.8" stroke="none"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="12" cy="5"  r="1.8" stroke="none"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="21" cy="18" r="1.8" stroke="none"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="7"  cy="12" r="1.2" stroke="none" opacity="0.75"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="17" cy="12" r="1.2" stroke="none" opacity="0.75"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 data-i18n="svc5_t">CX Operations</h3>
          <p data-i18n="svc5_p">Mapeo del journey del cliente, eliminación de cuellos de botella y procesos de soporte escalables.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Journey</span><span class="tag">Procesos</span><span class="tag">CX</span></div>
        </article>

        <article class="svc reveal">
          <div class="svc-glyph iris float">
            <div class="surface">
              <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path class="fill" stroke="none" d="M12 2.5 L13.5 10.5 L21.5 12 L13.5 13.5 L12 21.5 L10.5 13.5 L2.5 12 L10.5 10.5 Z"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="19.5" cy="4.5" r="1.1" stroke="none"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="4.5"  cy="19.5" r="1.1" stroke="none"/>
                <circle class="fill" cx="19.5" cy="19.5" r="0.7" stroke="none" opacity="0.7"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 data-i18n="svc6_t">AI Integration</h3>
          <p data-i18n="svc6_p">OpenAI, Whisper, pipelines generativos. IA como infraestructura del soporte, no como gimmick.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag">OpenAI</span><span class="tag">Whisper</span><span class="tag">LLM</span></div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════ PROJECTS ═══════════════════ -->
  <section id="projects" class="s">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="s-head reveal">
        <span class="label" data-i18n="lbl_proj">Proyectos · 03</span>
        <h2 data-i18n="proj_h"><span class="grad">Automatizaciones</span> reales.</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Primary: Automation/CX projects with modal -->
      <div class="projects">
        <article class="proj feature reveal proj-clickable" data-modal="jousfit">
          <div class="proj-top">
            <div class="proj-orb"><div class="surface"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 5 h16 a1 1 0 0 1 1 1 v9 a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1 h-9 l-4 4 v-4 h-3 a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1 v-9 a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1z"/><circle class="fill" cx="9" cy="10.5" r="1" stroke="none"/><circle class="fill" cx="12" cy="10.5" r="1" stroke="none"/><circle class="fill" cx="15" cy="10.5" r="1" stroke="none"/></svg></div></div>
            <div class="proj-client-badge">Interprika</div>
          </div>
          <span class="proj-num">01 · 2024–25</span>
          <h3>n8n JousFit</h3>
          <p data-i18n="p2d">Fitness ecommerce CRM: Chatwoot V0–V24, buffer humano, detección de fraude Shopify e IA conversacional. Tiempo de respuesta de 4 horas a 12 minutos.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag hot">n8n</span><span class="tag hot">OpenAI</span><span class="tag">Shopify</span><span class="tag">Chatwoot</span></div>
          <div class="proj-hint" data-i18n="proj_hint">Ver workflows →</div>
        </article>

        <article class="proj feature reveal proj-clickable" data-modal="bodas">
          <div class="proj-top">
            <div class="proj-orb"><div class="surface"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="1.7"/><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="1.7"/><circle cx="12" cy="18" r="1.7"/><path d="M7.7 7 L10.7 16.5"/><path d="M16.3 7 L13.3 16.5"/><path d="M8 6h8"/></svg></div></div>
            <div class="proj-client-badge">Interprika</div>
          </div>
          <span class="proj-num">02 · 2024</span>
          <h3>n8n Bodas.com.mx</h3>
          <p data-i18n="p1d">Automatización completa para gestión de eventos: scraping, email tracking y CRM sync. La planner pasó de "creo que tengo 200 leads" a una lista real, dateada y scoreada.</p>
          <div class="tags"><span class="tag hot">n8n</span><span class="tag">Scraping</span><span class="tag">Monday.com</span><span class="tag">WhatsApp</span></div>
          <div class="proj-hint" data-i18n="proj_hint">Ver workflows →</div>
        </article>

      </div>

      <!-- Secondary: web/other projects — compact list -->
      <div class="proj-secondary reveal">
        <div class="ps-divider"><span data-i18n="ps_otros">otros proyectos · web &amp; dev</span></div>
        <div class="ps-list">
          <div class="ps-item">
            <span class="ps-num">03</span>
            <span class="ps-info">
              <span class="ps-name">AHF Jamaica</span>
              <span class="ps-tags">WordPress · SEO</span>
            </span>
            <span class="ps-metric" data-i18n="ps_ahf">+230% tráfico orgánico</span>
          </div>
          <a class="ps-item" href="https://paragonisg.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="ps-num">04</span>
            <span class="ps-info">
              <span class="ps-name">Paragon ISG</span>
              <span class="ps-tags">WordPress · Corporate</span>
            </span>
            <span class="ps-metric" data-i18n="ps_paragon">3 RFPs en 60 días</span>
            <span class="ps-arr">↗</span>
          </a>
          <a class="ps-item" href="https://github.com/scampt/vantageWPRedirect" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="ps-num">05</span>
            <span class="ps-info">
              <span class="ps-name">VantageWP Redirect</span>
              <span class="ps-tags">WordPress · Plugin · UTM</span>
            </span>
            <span class="ps-metric" data-i18n="ps_vwp">6 sitios en producción</span>
            <span class="ps-arr">↗</span>
          </a>
          <a class="ps-item" href="https://scampt.github.io/LutherAlien/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="ps-num">06</span>
            <span class="ps-info">
              <span class="ps-name">LutherAlien</span>
              <span class="ps-tags">NFT · Web3 · Experimental</span>
            </span>
            <span class="ps-metric" data-i18n="ps_luther">Landing + wallet connect</span>
            <span class="ps-arr">↗</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════ PROJECT MODAL ═══════════════════ -->
  <div class="proj-modal-overlay" id="proj-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Detalle de proyecto">
    <div class="proj-modal-box" id="proj-modal-box">
      <button class="proj-modal-close" id="proj-modal-close" aria-label="Cerrar">
        <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div id="proj-modal-content"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Modal templates ─── -->

  <template id="tpl-jousfit">
    <div class="modal-head">
      <div class="modal-title-row">
        <h2 class="modal-title">n8n JousFit</h2>
        <span class="modal-client-tag">Interprika · 2024–25</span>
      </div>
      <p class="modal-subtitle" data-i18n="m_jousfit_sub">CRM + Chatbot + Ecommerce Automation</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-gallery" id="modal-gallery-jousfit">
      <div class="gal-track">
        <div class="gal-slide active">
          <img src="/workflows/jousfit-1.png" alt="V2 Human Handoff — lógica de traspaso agente humano" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="gal-caption" data-i18n="gal_j1">1 · V2 Human Handoff — traspaso inteligente al equipo humano</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gal-slide">
          <img src="/workflows/jousfit-2.png" alt="V3 Orders — gestión completa de pedidos Shopify" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="gal-caption" data-i18n="gal_j2">2 · V3 Orders — gestión de pedidos Shopify end-to-end</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gal-slide">
          <img src="/workflows/jousfit-3.png" alt="Invoice Scrapper — extracción de facturas con IA" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="gal-caption" data-i18n="gal_j3">3 · Invoice Scrapper — extracción automática de facturas con IA</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gal-slide">
          <img src="/workflows/jousfit-4.png" alt="V18 AI Agent — agente conversacional con memoria" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="gal-caption" data-i18n="gal_j4">4 · V18 AI Agent — agente IA con herramientas y memoria por cliente</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gal-slide">
          <img src="/workflows/jousfit-5.png" alt="Puerta de Fraude — validación Shopify + Cubbo" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="gal-caption" data-i18n="gal_j5">5 · Puerta de Fraude — validación pre-despacho Shopify + Cubbo</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="gal-controls">
        <button class="gal-btn gal-prev" aria-label="Anterior">
          <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="gal-dots">
          <span class="gal-dot active"></span>
          <span class="gal-dot"></span>
          <span class="gal-dot"></span>
          <span class="gal-dot"></span>
          <span class="gal-dot"></span>
        </div>
        <button class="gal-btn gal-next" aria-label="Siguiente">
          <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <p data-i18n="m_jousfit_desc">Sistema CRM completo para fitness ecommerce. 68+ workflows en producción: chatbot V0–V24 en Chatwoot con buffer humano en Redis, detección de fraude en pedidos Shopify + Cubbo, agente IA conversacional con memoria persistente por cliente, y extracción de facturas con OpenAI. Tiempo de primera respuesta: de 4h a 12min.</p>
      <div class="modal-metrics">
        <div class="modal-metric"><span class="mm-n">4h → 12min</span><span class="mm-l" data-i18n="m_response">Tiempo de respuesta</span></div>
        <div class="modal-metric"><span class="mm-n">68+</span><span class="mm-l" data-i18n="m_wf">Workflows</span></div>
        <div class="modal-metric"><span class="mm-n">V0→V24</span><span class="mm-l">Chatwoot</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-stack-row">
        <span class="tag hot">n8n</span><span class="tag hot">OpenAI</span><span class="tag">Chatwoot</span><span class="tag">Shopify</span><span class="tag">Supabase</span><span class="tag">Redis</span><span class="tag">WhatsApp API</span><span class="tag">Cubbo</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-foot">
      <a class="modal-link" href="https://github.com/scampt/n8n-jousfit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
        GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </template>

  <template id="tpl-bodas">
    <div class="modal-head">
      <div class="modal-title-row">
